_sText:
Hey!

This is my first released Jail Map.
It's called ba_jail_Sunny_Place because the Map is based on ba_jail_summer.
I tried to optimized the Map as much as possible.
It have High FPS(100-150) and it has a good Gameplay.
I recommened to play this Map with up to 20 Players.

-Secret Spots and Ways
-Balanced
-Funny
-High Fps(100-150)
-Detailed
-Funny Games like Football, Swimming Pool, etc...

!!!! FPS-CRASH AT BEGINNING OF MAP IS FIXED !!!!
(Fixed Map Crash)
